# AI Waiter Backend API

## Base URL

```txt
http://localhost:4000
```

---

# 1. Get restaurant tables

## Endpoint

```txt
GET /restaurants/:slug/tables
```

## Example

```txt
GET /restaurants/ai-demo/tables
```

## Response

```json
[
  {
    "id": "db003f6a-120b-4e0d-b526-cf676d9f8a00",
    "number": 3,
    "seats": 4,
    "status": "FREE",
    "posX": 50,
    "posY": 10
  }
]
```

---

# 2. Reserve table

## Endpoint

```txt
POST /tables/:id/reserve
```

## Body

```json
{
  "partySize": 2
}
```

## Example

```txt
POST /tables/db003f6a-120b-4e0d-b526-cf676d9f8a00/reserve
```

## Response

```json
{
  "sessionId": "5a30521e-13de-4a0b-8284-94157fe21a3c",
  "table": {
    "id": "db003f6a-120b-4e0d-b526-cf676d9f8a00",
    "number": 3,
    "status": "RESERVED"
  },
  "assistantMessage": "Your table 3 is reserved."
}
```

---

# 3. Send chat message

## Endpoint

```txt
POST /chat/message
```

## Body

```json
{
  "sessionId": "5a30521e-13de-4a0b-8284-94157fe21a3c",
  "message": "What do you recommend?"
}
```

## Response

```json
{
  "sessionId": "5a30521e-13de-4a0b-8284-94157fe21a3c",
  "answer": "Hello! I am your AI waiter from n8n."
}
```

---

# 4. Get chat messages

## Endpoint

```txt
GET /chat/sessions/:sessionId/messages
```

## Example

```txt
GET /chat/sessions/5a30521e-13de-4a0b-8284-94157fe21a3c/messages
```

## Response

```json
[
  {
    "sender": "CUSTOMER",
    "content": "Hello"
  },
  {
    "sender": "AI",
    "content": "Hello! I am your AI waiter."
  }
]
```

---

# N8N Webhook Payload

NestJS sends this payload to n8n:

```json
{
  "sessionId": "5a30521e-13de-4a0b-8284-94157fe21a3c",
  "restaurantId": "3b0c9396-1dda-44ee-8f79-65dff8d65432",
  "tableId": "db003f6a-120b-4e0d-b526-cf676d9f8a00",
  "tableNumber": 3,
  "partySize": 2,
  "message": "What do you recommend?"
}
```

---

# Expected n8n response

```json
{
  "answer": "I recommend pasta and lemonade."
}
```
